file: RoutedCommand.php
class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Domain\\Command\\RoutedCommand"
type: readonly final class
summary: "RoutedCommand is a readonly value object representing a command in the domain layer, distinguishing between core and extension command types. It encapsulates the command kind, payload, options, and status to provide a structured representation of domain operations."
